  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras/def5fca0a2cbf890b6ad32032efb726c.avif?t=1759712565\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras_big/def5fca0a2cbf890b6ad32032efb726c.avif?t=1759712565 width=800 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon waking in the eerie, fog-enshrouded universe of Silent Siren, Dex Mercer finds himself holding a mysterious radio, guided to mysterious buttons around the world by an familiar friend, named Larse. With no memory of how he arrived, Dex is on a quest to uncover the chilling mysteries of the town and face the haunting truths of his past, all while the spectral voice of his wife.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras/2576b59857c13921cda11152d1350525.avif?t=1759712565\" width=230 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape Rooms (Playable but Under Construction):</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay the levels from the single player with an escape room twist. Unlock your way to a special bonus levels. Featuring a 1:1 recreation of Terciera, Azores, Portugal, where the solo developer experience real paranormal activities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras/b00de24855cbeae392b9d78b43723aa2.avif?t=1759712565\" width=230 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hockey Ministicks VR (easter Egg)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes - Online hockey as well as air hockey and more mini games are featured in the game. This is the full game of Hockey Ministicks VR.<br><br>Join The Discord<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>3d artist credits </u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>ring</i></u></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras/def5fca0a2cbf890b6ad32032efb726c.avif?t=1759712565\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras_big/def5fca0a2cbf890b6ad32032efb726c.avif?t=1759712565 width=800 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon waking in the eerie, fog-enshrouded universe of Silent Siren, Dex Mercer finds himself holding a mysterious radio, guided to mysterious buttons around the world by an familiar friend, named Larse. With no memory of how he arrived, Dex is on a quest to uncover the chilling mysteries of the town and face the haunting truths of his past, all while the spectral voice of his wife.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras/2576b59857c13921cda11152d1350525.avif?t=1759712565\" width=230 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape Rooms (Playable but Under Construction):</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay the levels from the single player with an escape room twist. Unlock your way to a special bonus levels. Featuring a 1:1 recreation of Terciera, Azores, Portugal, where the solo developer experience real paranormal activities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815470/extras/b00de24855cbeae392b9d78b43723aa2.avif?t=1759712565\" width=230 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hockey Ministicks VR (easter Egg)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes - Online hockey as well as air hockey and more mini games are featured in the game. This is the full game of Hockey Ministicks VR.<br><br>Join The Discord<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>3d artist credits </u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>ring</i></u></p>",
